title: Statement by NSC Spokesperson Emily Horne on National Security Advisor Jake Sullivanâ€™s Call with Ibrahim Kalin, Spokesperson and Chief Advisor to the President of Turkey | The White House
content: National Security Advisor Jake Sullivan spoke by phone today with Ibrahim Kalin, Spokesperson and Chief Advisor to the President of Turkey. Following the meeting between President Joe Biden and President Recep Tayyip Erdogan on June 14, Mr. Sullivan and Dr. Kalin discussed a range of regional issues.###
